      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHAPPY'S TOTEM (6) was a winner two back but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 6 length third at this track (22.96). Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can measure up this time. ARGYLE EMMA (4) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Filled a minor placings again last time when second (22.50) at Ballarat making it five placings in a row. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Bold showing expected. MOTIVATE (3) was unwanted in betting last start but proved too quick with an all-the-way win over 450m at Warrnambool in a Bottom Up - Grade 5, scoring by one length (25.85). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expected to feature again. AXEL'S RADAR (1) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
